      "name": "Monte Carlo UQ coverage check — hemolysis prediction intervals",
      "description": "500-sample Monte Carlo propagation of inlet velocity, fluid viscosity, and power-law exponent uncertainty was performed. Coverage probability of 95 % prediction intervals was 97.3 % against the in-vitro dataset, exceeding the 90 % minimum.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/monte-carlo-uq-propagation-2025"
    }
  ],
